    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small scissors having a form specialized for cutting appliqués and other small, negative shapes; often has one round-backed blade against a short, straight blade.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
